company.name: EQUANS Services a.s.
company.description:
EQUANS Services a.s. is a specialist  in comprehensive energy solutions providing broad range of services in area of  electrical installations in industrial and energy sectors, smart building technologies, implementation of complete plants, engineering, automation and facility management. With almost 400 experienced employees  they generated  revenues of CZK 1.5 billion.
EQUANS Services a.s. is part of the French group EQUANS, which is a global energy player and an expert operator in the three key sectors of electricity, natural gas and energy services. The Group supports changes in society that are based as much on economic growth as on  social progress and the preservation of natural resources. Rising energy needs have pushed EQUANS to accelerate its investment policy in an effort to become a leader in the transfer to clean energy by focusing its strategy on energy efficiency, renewable energy, and new business.
